---
---

<section class="w-full bg-white py-24 md:py-32 px-6 flex justify-center" id="methodology">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] w-full flex flex-col gap-16 md:gap-24">
    
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 text-center">
      <span class="text-[#3cbce6] text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">Methodology</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-[#1e293b] font-serif" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
        How the Gold is Made
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- 3-Column Staggered Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 md:gap-8 xl:gap-14">
      
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col group">
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5] bg-[#e2e8f0] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-6 md:mb-8 shadow-sm">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507149833220-4a8ce32488d0?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" 
            alt="Abstract ideation texture" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out opacity-90 mix-blend-luminosity" 
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#cbd5e1]/30 group-hover:bg-[#cbd5e1]/10 transition-colors duration-500"></div>
          <span class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-white font-serif italic text-6xl md:text-7xl mix-blend-overlay opacity-80" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">01</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[22px] text-[#1e293b] font-serif italic mb-3" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Descent</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          Before anything is made, something must be entered. We go down —
          into the question, into the discomfort, into the part of the brief
          that no one wanted to say out loud. That is where the work begins.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 (Staggered Down) -->
      <div class="flex flex-col group md:mt-24">
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5] bg-[#f8fafc] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-6 md:mb-8 shadow-md">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518640467707-6811f4a6ab73?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" 
            alt="Abstract curation texture" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out opacity-60" 
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/20 group-hover:bg-white/0 transition-colors duration-500"></div>
          <span class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-white font-serif italic text-6xl md:text-7xl drop-shadow-sm opacity-90" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">02</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[22px] text-[#1e293b] font-serif italic mb-3" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Pressure</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          Gold is not found — it is made. By heat, by weight, by the slow
          violence of everything unnecessary being forced out. We sit inside
          that pressure until only what is true remains.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col group">
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5] bg-[#89a89c] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-6 md:mb-8 shadow-sm">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533560904424-a0c61dc306fc?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" 
            alt="Abstract realization texture" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out opacity-60 mix-blend-overlay" 
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#6b8b7e]/40 group-hover:bg-[#6b8b7e]/20 transition-colors duration-500 mix-blend-color"></div>
          <span class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-white font-serif italic text-6xl md:text-7xl drop-shadow-md opacity-90" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">03</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[22px] text-[#1e293b] font-serif italic mb-3" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Emergence</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          What surfaces is never what we planned. It is what survived
          the process — quieter than expected, heavier than it looks,
          and somehow already familiar, the way all true things are
          when you finally stop looking for them.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>